create a database with the following table setup:

mysql> desc books;
+--------+--------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| Field  | Type         | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
+--------+--------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| id     | char(56)     | NO   | PRI | NULL    |       |
| title  | varchar(255) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| author | varchar(100) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
+--------+--------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
3 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> desc clips;
+--------------+--------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| Field        | Type         | Null | Key | Default | Extra          |
+--------------+--------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| id           | int(10)      | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| book         | char(56)     | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
| location     | int(6)       | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
| entry_header | varchar(255) | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
| hash_id      | char(56)     | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
| quote        | longtext     | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
+--------------+--------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
6 rows in set (0.01 sec)


